	<text>
		<body>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Cleved</placeName> <date>Apr 12 1861</date></p>
				<p>Rev &#38; Dear Friend</p>
			<p rend="indent(3)">I send you herewith<lb/> a brief history respecting the grand<lb/> metamorphose of the Tif<add>&#63;</add> Israel Kabal<lb/> into a demi&#45;semi&#45;Gentile and<lb/> Jew church.  Before coming to<lb/> preliminary trial of the rejunction<add>&#63;</add><lb/> last <date>Wednesday</date> the Trustees<lb/> stepped forward &#38; compromised<lb/> with me indemnifying me for my<lb/> loss of seats&#8212;I took by the advice<lb/> of my lawyer one of the best in<lb/> the State half of the original cost of<lb/> my seats &#38; have quitted the<lb/> Kabal forever.  I shall shortly<lb/> unite myself with the old Congrega<lb/>&#45;tion Anslie Chesed and trust to<lb/> accomplish something <hi rend="underline">there</hi>&#44; worthy<lb/> the good cause.  If you cannot insert<lb/> the enclosed article please send it<lb/> to the Jewish Messenger as I am determined<lb/> to have a public statement made of the<lb/> affair.  I hope you will find room in your<lb/> valuable journal.  More anon&#160;&#160;In haste</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">Yours truly&#160;&#160;<persName role="author">B. F. Peixotto</persName></p>
		</body>
	</text>
